                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-522" type="given" value="EDWIN"></interp>EDWIN LOCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I slept in this room—I had this coat there, and missed it—I found the prisoner on the lower flight of stairs with the coat on—I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184003020083"></xptr>
               <p>asked what he did with it—he said, merely to keep himself warm—this hat was on his head, his own hat was up-stairs, and it was worse than this.</p>
